Pandemic Experiment Scenario (PES) - RL-Agent Version
======================================================

A single RL-Agent autonomous resource allocation system for pandemic mitigation.

The PES system implements a reinforcement learning agent that:
- Allocates resources to mitigate city severity in real-time
- Learns optimal allocation strategies through trial-and-error
- Operates autonomously without human interaction or GUI

Structure:
  - Blocks: 8 collections of sequences
  - Sequences: 8 maps per block
  - Trials: Variable number of cities per sequence
  - Total: ~360 trials per experiment

Configuration:
  - See PES/config/CONFIG.py for detailed parameter settings
  - System runs in autonomous RL-Agent mode only
  
Execution:
  python3 -m PES
